Date: Thu 11 Nov 2021
Source: OIE, WAHID (World Animal Health Information Database) reports, 2021 [edited]
https://wahis.oie.int/#/report-info?reportId=42537


_Brucella melitensis_ (Inf. with), France
-----------------------------------------
Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Started: 12 Oct 2021
Confirmed: 20 Oct 2021
Reported: 11 Nov 2021
Reason for notification: Recurrence
Last occurrence: 31 Mar 2013
Causal agent: _Brucella melitensis_
Nature of diagnosis: Laboratory
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

New outbreaks
Summary of outbreaks
Total outbreaks (1)
Outbreak location 1: Saint Laurent en Faucigny, Bonneville, Haute-Savoie, Auvergne-Rhone-Alpes
Started: 12 Oct 2021
Epidemiological unit: farm
Total animals affected:
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Killed and disposed of / Slaughtered or killed for commercial use / Vaccinated
Cattle / 219 / 1 / 0 / 0 / 1 / 0
Affected population: dairy cattle, a first test on bulk milk gives a non-negative result. The herd is blocked and the milk is pasteurized until a _Brucella melitensis_ PCR test is carried out. The epidemiological investigation to understand the infection is underway. All the linked animals and herds are identified and placed under surveillance.

Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: Unknown or inconclusive, contact with wild species

Control measures at the event level
Domestic control measures to be applied: traceability; movement control inside the country ante- and post-mortem inspections; official destruction of animals products; disinfection; stamping out

Additional control measures different from event level: Surveillance outside containment and or the protection zone

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type/ Species / Test / Test date / Result
ANSES (Agence nationale de sécurité sanitaire des aliments et de l'environnement) - Laboratoire de santé animale de Maisons-Alfort National Laboratory / Cattle / Bacterial culture / 8 Nov 2021 / Positive

LIDAL (Laboratoire d'analyses biologiques et alimentaires) de Haute-Savoie Local Laboratory/ Cattle / Milk enzyme-linked immunosorbent assay (Milk ELISA) / 20 Oct 2021 / Positive

ANSES (Agence nationale de sécurité sanitaire des aliments et de l'environnement) - Laboratoire de santé animale de Maisons-Alfort National Laboratory / Cattle / Polymerase chain reaction (PCR) / 9 Nov 2021 / Positive

ANSES (Agence nationale de sécurité sanitaire des aliments et de l'environnement) - Laboratoire de santé animale de Maisons-Alfort National Laboratory / Cattle / Milk ring test (MRT) / 12 Oct 2021 / Positive

